  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00001",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "关平上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00002",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "关平"
      ],
      "text": "身披铠甲逞英雄，小将原来有父风。却喜趋庭承亲训，须知子孝与臣忠。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00003",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关平"
      ],
      "text": "小将关平，今日父王升座，只得在此伺侯。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00004",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "关羽内嗽。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00005",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关平"
      ],
      "text": "道犹未了，父王出堂来也。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00006",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "关羽上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00007",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "器宇昂昂志气舒，指天化日定规模。荆州久镇无人犯，认取须眉大丈夫。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00008",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关平"
      ],
      "text": "父王在上，臣儿打恭。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00009",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "我儿免礼，坐了。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00010",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关平"
      ],
      "text": "谢坐。请问父王，当今天下鼎足三分，臣儿不知，请父王试说一遍，臣儿洗耳恭听。",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00011",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "我儿听者。当今天下鼎足三分，曹操占据中原，孙权霸住江东，你伯父首尊西蜀，这都是汉家天下也。",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00012",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "粉蝶儿",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "那其间，楚汉争强，叹周秦早属刘项。分君臣，先到咸阳。一个儿拔山力，一个儿量宽容海。他两个，一时开剏，想当日，黄阁乌江。一个儿，用了三杰，一个儿立诛八将。",
      "text_length": 76
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00013",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "沉醉东风",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "一个在短剑下身亡，一个儿听静鞭三下响。这的是祖宗传位与儿孙，到今日只落得享、享。",
      "text_length": 40
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00014",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "献帝——",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00015",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "沉醉东风",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "他无靠无依，董卓不仁不义；",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00016",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "吕布——",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00017",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "沉醉东风",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "一冲一撞。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00018",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关平"
      ],
      "text": "请问父王，当初桃园结义之事，臣儿不知，请父王试说一遍。",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00019",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "吾儿听者。当初桃园结义之时，宰白马祭天，杀乌牛祭地。不求同日生，只愿同日死，一在三在，一亡三亡。",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00020",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "十二月",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "想当日，兄弟在范阳，兄长在楼桑；俺关某在蒲州解良；更有那，诸葛在南阳。煞时间，英雄出四方。结义了皇叔与关张，",
      "text_length": 54
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00021",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "尧民歌",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "其年三谒卧龙岗，已料定，鼎足三分，汉家邦。俺哥哥，称孤道寡世无双。俺关某，匹马单刀镇荆襄。长也么江，今经几战场。",
      "text_length": 56
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00022",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "却正是后浪——",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00023",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "尧民歌",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "催前浪。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00024",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "中军上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00025",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "中军"
      ],
      "text": "猛虎台前出入，貔貅帐内传宣。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00026",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "中军"
      ],
      "text": "中军叩头。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00027",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "中军。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00028",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "中军"
      ],
      "text": "吓。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00029",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "无有某家将令，为何私离汛地？",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00030",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "中军"
      ],
      "text": "东吴鲁大夫差人下书。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00031",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "那下书人呢？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00032",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "中军"
      ],
      "text": "现在帐外。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00033",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "与我搜检明白，抓他进来，",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00034",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "中军"
      ],
      "text": "领命。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00035",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "周仓。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00036",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周仓"
      ],
      "text": "在。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00037",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "传鼓开门。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00038",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周仓"
      ],
      "text": "传鼓开门。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00039",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖大开门〗。关羽归大座。中军领黄文同上。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00040",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "中军"
      ],
      "text": "下书人当面。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00041",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄文"
      ],
      "text": "下书人与爷叩头。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00042",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "下书人，你叫什么名字？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00043",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄文"
      ],
      "text": "我叫大胆黄文。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00044",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "你的胆有多大？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00045",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄文"
      ],
      "text": "有巴斗大。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00046",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "周仓。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00047",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周仓"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00048",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "剖腹看者！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00049",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄文"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀爷呀，我的胆没那么大，有荠莱仔那么大。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00050",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "为何能大能小？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00051",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄文"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀，能强能弱我的爷。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00052",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "收！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00053",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "周仓收刀。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00054",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "可有书信？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00055",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄文"
      ],
      "text": "书信呈上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00056",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "原来是鲁大夫请某过江赴会。俺这里修书不及，原书发回。回去奏明你家爷，说某本月十三日亲自过江赴会。放他出去。",
      "text_length": 53
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00057",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周仓"
      ],
      "text": "出去！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00058",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄文"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00059",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "黄文"
      ],
      "text": "今日吓破黄文胆，再也不做下书人。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00060",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "黄文"
      ],
      "text": "好怕，好怕。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00061",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "黄文下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00062",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "掩门。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00063",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "周仓"
      ],
      "text": "掩门。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00064",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖大开门〗。四龙套自两边分下，关羽转小座。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00065",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关平"
      ],
      "text": "父王，那书信上写的什么言语，说与臣儿知道。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00066",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "我儿听者。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00067",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "石榴花",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "上写着，两朝相隔汉阳江。又写着，鲁肃请云长。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00068",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关平"
      ],
      "text": "安排什么来？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00069",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "石榴花",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "安排下筵宴不寻常，再休想，画堂别是风光。哪里有凤凰杯满捧葡萄酿，尽都是巴豆共着砒霜。玳宴前摆列着尽都是英雄将，再休想，开宴出红妆。",
      "text_length": 65
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00070",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "斗鹌鹁",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "安排下，打凤的牢笼。准备着天罗地网。哪里有待客的筵席？分明是杀人、杀人的战场。再休想重意诚心，全不怕后人来讲。",
      "text_length": 55
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00071",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关平"
      ],
      "text": "古来筵无好筵，会无好会，还是不去的是。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00072",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "斗鹌鹑",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "既然他谨谨的相邀，",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00073",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
