      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "上下楼",
      "speakers": [
        "关羽"
      ],
      "text": "恁道是，隔大江起战场，都急难亲傍。着那厮鞠躬身，送某到船上。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901101_e00082",
      "play_id": "70901101",
      "scene_id": "70901101_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
